---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof for Roofers — Testimonials That Win the Big Jobs | SocialProof" description="Roofers: roofing is a high-ticket, high-trust sale. SocialProof helps you collect and display customer testimonials so homeowners choose you over every other estimate.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Roofers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        A new roof is one of the biggest purchases a homeowner makes. Before they sign any contract, they're reading every review they can find. SocialProof helps you collect customer testimonials and display them on your website — so when they compare three estimates, yours is the one they trust.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Why roofing testimonials close more estimates</h2>
      <p>Roofing is a high-ticket, infrequent purchase. Homeowners have no baseline for what "good" looks like — so they lean heavily on social proof. A contractor with a dozen visible testimonials on their website looks dramatically more credible than one with the same services and a better price but no visible track record.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">SocialProof gives you a widget that collects testimonials via a simple share link (text or email after job completion) and displays them on your site automatically. No login required for customers. Takes five minutes to set up.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What makes roofing testimonials convert</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Specificity:</strong> "They replaced our 30-year-old roof in one day, cleaned up every nail, and came in under estimate."</li>
        <li><strong>Stress relief:</strong> "We had damage from the storm and were overwhelmed — they walked us through the insurance claim and handled everything."</li>
        <li><strong>Trust in workmanship:</strong> "Two years later, no leaks, no issues. Worth every penny."</li>
        <li><strong>Professionalism:</strong> "On time, no mess left behind, crew was respectful of our property."</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">These aren't reviews you can fake. They're exactly what the next homeowner getting three estimates needs to read before choosing you.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How it works for roofing businesses</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>After job completion, send your customer a SocialProof share link (one click, no account needed)</li>
        <li>They submit their testimonial — text, optionally with a photo of the finished roof</li>
        <li>You approve and publish it to your website widget instantly</li>
        <li>Every estimate page, landing page, and homepage shows real social proof from real customers</li>
      </ol>

      <div style="background:#f8f9fa;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Free forever for 1 active widget</h3>
        <p style="color:#555;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Start collecting and displaying roofing testimonials today. No credit card. No expiration. Upgrade when you want more widgets or advanced features.</p>
        <a href="https://socialproof.dev/signup" style="display:inline-block;background:#0070f3;color:#fff;padding:0.75rem 1.75rem;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">Start free — takes 5 minutes</a>
      </div>

      <section style="margin-top:3rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Frequently asked questions</h2>

        <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
          "@context": "https://schema.org",
          "@type": "FAQPage",
          "mainEntity": [
            {
              "@type": "Question",
              "name": "How do I collect testimonials from roofing customers?",
              "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "SocialProof generates a simple share link you can text or email after each job. Customers click it, write their testimonial (no account needed), and submit. Takes them less than two minutes."
              }
            },
            {
              "@type": "Question",
              "name": "Can roofing testimonials help me win more estimates?",
              "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "Yes. When homeowners are comparing three contractors with similar prices, visible testimonials on your website are often the deciding factor. They reduce perceived risk on a high-ticket purchase."
              }
            },
            {
              "@type": "Question",
              "name": "Do I need a website to use SocialProof for my roofing business?",
              "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "You need a website to embed the testimonial widget. It works with any site — Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, or a custom HTML site. A simple one-page site is enough."
              }
            }
          ]
        })}>
        </script>

        <details style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:8px;padding:1rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
          <summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;">How do I collect testimonials from roofing customers?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;color:#555;">SocialProof generates a simple share link you can text or email after each job. Customers click it, write their testimonial (no account needed), and submit. Takes them less than two minutes.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:8px;padding:1rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
          <summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;">Can roofing testimonials help me win more estimates?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;color:#555;">Yes. When homeowners are comparing three contractors with similar prices, visible testimonials on your website are often the deciding factor. They reduce perceived risk on a high-ticket purchase.</p>
        </details>
        <details style="border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:8px;padding:1rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">
          <summary style="font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;">Do I need a website to use SocialProof for my roofing business?</summary>
          <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;color:#555;">You need a website to embed the testimonial widget. It works with any site — Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, or a custom HTML site. A simple one-page site is enough.</p>
        </details>
      </section>
    </section>
  </main>

